Nature Step

Through this ancient ritual, the druid may become
one with his immediate surroundings, gaining the
ability to sink into the ground and reappear a
short distance away at will.  That effect makes
it nearly impossible to melee with the affected
druid.

Command: naturestep
Base Cost: 25 SP
Base Recovery: medium
Base Effect: protection (high)
Base Duration: short
Guild Level: 13
